         <div class="sqs-layout sqs-grid-12 columns-12" data-type="page" data-updated-on="1582547353244" id="page-5e3c0bb5a9f1571c8eebd698"><div class="row sqs-row"><div class="col sqs-col-12 span-12"><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html" data-block-type="2" id="block-addc1751e9ccdd21353c"><div class="sqs-block-content"><h1 style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;">剑桥全球论坛 (CGC)</h1></div></div><div class="row sqs-row"><div class="col sqs-col-2 span-2"><div class="sqs-block spacer-block sqs-block-spacer sized vsize-1" data-block-type="21" id="block-6493da73d1ba4d6a65c9"><div class="sqs-block-content">&nbsp;</div></div></div><div class="col sqs-col-8 span-8"><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html" data-block-type="2" id="block-890437c62c841aa1d9e3"><div class="sqs-block-content"><p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class="">剑桥全球论坛总部位于英国剑桥大学，旨在就无法单靠个别国家或少数国家群体的能力解决的全球性问题进行探讨与传播，设立对话平台。不同时代的思想领袖聚集一堂，在对话中就复杂的全球性挑战分享他们的见解，引发公众的思考与反思，并引导制定应对方案。</p></div></div></div><div class="col sqs-col-2 span-2"><div class="sqs-block spacer-block sqs-block-spacer sized vsize-1" data-block-type="21" id="block-a38fc40da89e2fe43f03"><div class="sqs-block-content">&nbsp;</div></div></div></div><div class="sqs-block video-block sqs-block-video" data-block-json="&#123;&quot;blockAnimation&quot;:&quot;none&quot;,&quot;layout&quot;:&quot;caption-below&quot;,&quot;overlay&quot;:false,&quot;description&quot;:&#123;&quot;html&quot;:&quot;&lt;p class=\&quot;\&quot;&gt;\u57282019\u5E747\u6708\u7684\u201CCGC\u6C14\u5019\u53D8\u5316\u4E0E\u4F26\u7406\u539F\u5219\u201D\u6D3B\u52A8\u5F00\u59CB\u524D\uFF0C\u9A6C\u4E01\u00B7\u91CC\u65AF\u52CB\u7235\u4E0E\u5251\u6865\u5927\u5B66\u7814\u7A76\u751FMorgan Sheil\u5DF2\u7ECF\u5C31\u6C14\u5019\u7684\u8BDD\u9898\u8FDB\u884C\u4E86\u5168\u65B9\u4F4D\u7684\u63A2\u8BA8\u3002\uFF08\u66F4\u591A\u6709\u5173\u6C14\u5019\u53D8\u5316\u4F26\u7406\u539F\u5219\u3001\u6C14\u5019\u7ECF\u6D4E\u5B66\u7B49\u8BDD\u9898\u7684\u89C6\u9891\uFF0C